title: Did Paden's birthday video show without a mask in 2020?
subtitle: A viral tweet with a video says, "They tell us to stay away from society and wear a mask! But as you can see... they're not! It's all lies to control us!"
author: Jordan Liles
vclaim: The video of President-elect Joe Biden celebrating his birthday with a bunch of maskless people in 2020 was shown.
